magically answer your prayer

25:32.420 --> 25:33.685
20 years later.

25:34.888 --> 25:37.255
[ sniffles ]
all those bad feelings,

25:37.257 --> 25:39.890
We wasted so much time
being angry at each other.

25:39.892 --> 25:42.792
And I don't know why
I didn't forgive her sooner.

25:42.794 --> 25:44.927
You loved your mother.

25:44.929 --> 25:48.196
